data.description: Nestled in the heart of the Lincolnshire Historic District, this beautifully remodeled 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home epitomizes modern elegance and timeless charm. The interior design, expertly curated by Michael Carron, fosters a welcoming and spacious ambiance ideal for relaxation and entertaining.  Featuring a main-level master suite and three additional bedrooms upstairs, along with an exquisite kitchen boasting Café appliances, this residence strikes a harmonious balance between style and practicality, catering to the needs of today's discerning homeowner.
